Opportunity in perspective











5,000+
More than 5,000 brands entrust us to deliver essential communications to their clients, creating richer customer experiences.




$5T
Firms rely on us to process, on average, more than $5 Trillion fixed income and equity trades every day in North America.




95%
Want a clear picture of investor behavior? Clients look to us to provide visibility into the distribution of 95% of all ETF assets and 90% of all long-term mutual fund assets.










